author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Franklin Resources Announces Month-End Assets Under Management
text:
May 8 (Reuters) - Franklin Resources Inc:
* FRANKLIN RESOURCES, INC. ANNOUNCES MONTH-END ASSETS UNDER MANAGEMENT
* FRANKLIN RESOURCES INC - PRELIMINARY MONTH-END ASSETS UNDER MANAGEMENT OF $732.5 BILLION AT APRIL 30, 2018, COMPARED TO $737.5 BILLION AT MARCH 31, 2018
* FRANKLIN RESOURCES INC - PRELIMINARY AVERAGE ASSETS UNDER MANAGEMENT FOR QUARTER, THROUGH APRIL 30, 2018, WERE $735.0 BILLION Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
